  "description": "A vibrant and spectacular fireworks display illuminates the night sky above a cityscape and a long bridge spanning a dark body of water. The fireworks are bursting in a complex pattern of white, gold, and red streaks, creating a dazzling focal point. Below, the city skyline is visible with buildings lit up in varying degrees of brightness, forming a glowing backdrop. A prominent bridge with its lights reflecting on the water stretches into the distance, and hints of other structures suggest a bustling urban environment. The water is dark and calm, with sparse light reflections adding to the atmosphere. The image captures a celebratory moment with a sense of grandeur and festivity.",
